Distribution: Widely distributed and common in the warm and temperate parts of the Atlantic-, Indian-, and Pacific Oceans, usually between about 40°N and 40°S including also the Mediterranean, usually in large numbers ( Kramp, 1965 ; Fagetti, 1973 ; Bouillon, 1978b ; Goy, 1979 ; Navas-Pereira &Vannuci, 1991;
Pagès et al., 1992
;
Nagata et al., 2014
). Type locality: Mediterranean Sea, near the town of Nice.
